Since zenstruck/foundry 2.7: Proxy usage is deprecated in PHP 8.4. You should extend directly PersistentObjectFactory in your factories. Foundry now leverages the native PHP lazy system to auto-refresh objects (it can be enabled with "zenstruck_foundry.enable_auto_refresh_with_lazy_objects" configuration). See https://github.com/zenstruck/foundry/blob/2.x/UPGRADE-2.7.md to upgrade.
